data.description: Welcome to 726 Burksdale Road nestled in the heart of Norfolk's Desirable Colonial Heights neighborhood. LOAN ASSUMPTION OPPORTUNITY @ 2.25% VA Assumable loan to VA qualified buyer. Inquire about payoff. This home 3 bed, 2 bath Cape Cod offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and classic architectural details, making it a ideal home. 726 Burksdale was completely updated in 2020. Large Norfolk Backyard with a beautiful deck which has a covered portion where you can enjoy & relax during mornings or evenings. The Backyard is complete fenced in. Close proximity to Interstates, Downtown, Ocean View & Naval Station Norfolk make this home a phenomenal spot to land!
